                <h1>Can You Apply Peel and Stick Wallpaper Over Existing Wallpaper?</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper can be applied over existing wallpaper, but it's essential to ensure the surface is clean, smooth, and free of any texture. If your wallpaper has a glossy finish, consider lightly sanding it for better adhesion. This method is a quick way to refresh a space without the hassle of removing old wallpaper.</p>
